      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense. if I add the cost of the lost items to the COGS, the turnover ratio drops which is what I want to show. but i'm also trying to figure out how to categorize the cause in the report. right now it just says \"unexplained shrinkage.\" do you have any advice on how to frame the investigation into why this is happening or how to categorize these missing units in a professional way?",
